title: Emiliano Astorga
text: Emiliano Eduardo Astorga Lobos (born 21 September 1960) is a <a href="Chilean%20people">Chilean</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Manager%20%28association%20football%29">manager</a> and former player who played as a <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a>.
